import React from 'react'

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
    <Wrapper>
      <Title>SIGN IN</Title>
      <Form>
        <Input placeholder="user name" />
        <Input placeholder="password" />
   
        <Button>LOGIN</Button>
        <LINK>CREATE A NEW ACCOUNT</LINK>
      </Form>
    </Wrapper>
  </Container>
  )
}

export default Login
